{"tid":2284133,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"IKEA 宜家新出「冰狗」 引網民熱論打卡試食","createTime":"2020-11-13T05:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T03:27:42.000Z","uid":54373,"like":55,"dislike":273,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"7be084267950ee6bb73f99435920bec450cee696","tid":2284133,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2695000/2696484/coveridog_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2695000%2F2696484%2Fcoveridog_1024.jpg&h=2e2f0c33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港的 IKEA 宜家美食站經常會推出不同的新食品，深受消費者的喜愛。而中國內地的宜家美食站，亦推出不少吸引的食品，近日更推出與「熱狗」非常相似的食品 &mdash;「冰狗」，熱狗是將香腸夾在麵包中，而「冰狗」則是將雪糕取代香腸，夾在麵包中間，而此食品在推出沒多久，已經引來不少內地網民熱論。<br />\n<br />\n宜家美食站推出了新食品 &mdash; 「冰狗」，其英文名更是直接以中文翻譯成「Ice Dog」，售價為 3 元人民幣（約 HK$3.3）。而「冰狗」其實就是雪糕加上熱狗包，此款新奇有創意的食品吸引不少網民前往「打卡」，以及解鎖新食法。有網民更指「光看上去便覺得很好食」、「太有趣了，好想認識想到這個 Idea 的人」。"},{"pid":"f78986c45da8a0d2ba344c512add500f8de5ff56","tid":2284133,"uid":333969,"like":128,"dislike":0,"score":128,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:22:30.000Z","msg":"冰狗真的非常刺激！"},{"pid":"5f79137119da13297af006be63c08ad5313cd1db","tid":2284133,"uid":54373,"like":119,"dislike":2,"score":117,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"blue\">@連迪洛夫🇸🇪</span>"},{"pid":"5014217cbab3a62af67f78f33fb7ab6ac043f7ca","tid":2284133,"uid":199081,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:23:02.000Z","msg":"@連迪洛夫瑞典emoji"},{"pid":"fffb17818f6c7fe044473ac3bef28546af0c9a52","tid":2284133,"uid":127929,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:23:02.000Z","msg":"大陸人食開屎"},{"pid":"934930fedcd62355bae9b4d0d9851b22100145e0","tid":2284133,"uid":132557,"like":251,"dislike":3,"score":248,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"賣冰狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\