班身懷逾兩公斤冰毒，到尖沙嘴一酒店疑會合同黨時，遇上掃毒同袍，當場被捕，警方並在兩房間拘捕其餘兩名男女，包括警署警長的女友，至晚上警方再拘捕一名休班警員，以及在石硤尾起出二十三公斤冰毒，全部共逾二十五公斤總值一千七百多萬元，警方懷疑有人在早前大毒案中盜走證物轉售，事件令警隊「一哥」大為震怒及痛心。"},{"pid":"33f9d45ebfa89f0f2ea1ddee8d0ddac32d5f1a02","tid":2284133,"uid":185126,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:26:00.000Z","msg":"吱到成舊屎咁都拎黎做product shoot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cd66e31c4b763cab70188dce01f7c6c2104552","tid":2284133,"uid":29784,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"光看上去便覺得很好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305b2897b2e1c965251d19c6d90aa54476a6b7b6","tid":2284133,"uid":376010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:26:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b73aa862afd8a9b80610479ccf423e720e0a65fb","tid":2284133,"uid":225437,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"嘉頓忌廉bun啲friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43473615b0a32e3173e5ccfd4f9ee422bf95cf29","tid":2284133,"uid":154000,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:27:20.000Z","msg":"抄日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://digjapan.travel/zh_tw/spot/id=8070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdigjapan.travel%2Fzh_tw%2Fspot%2Fid%3D8070&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIpE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=2eb4dd96\" target=\"_blank\">https://digjapan.travel/zh_tw/spot/id=8070</a>"},{"pid":"c8cf457b6a83752e9704ce3b26bd01d61379e391","tid":2284133,"uid":260744,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:31:46.000Z","msg":"哦，你仆街喇，串呀sir食冰"},{"pid":"9a70e4e7c3cbe12ac329a3c7b0545d44b1ccf15e","tid":2284133,"uid":371,"like":56,"dislike":3,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T