ts/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:42:37.000Z","msg":"係大阪美國街食過<br />\n好撚好食<br />\n個包炸到熱辣辣同個雪糕好夾"},{"pid":"b9181fd48491f752558bb7873fbe5b26a2436363","tid":2284133,"uid":217822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7be084267950ee6bb73f99435920bec450cee696","tid":2284133,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2695000/2696484/coveridog_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2695000%2F2696484%2Fcoveridog_1024.jpg&h=2e2f0c33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港的 IKEA 宜家美食站經常會推出不同的新食品，深受消費者的喜愛。而中國內地的宜家美食站，亦推出不少吸引的食品，近日更推出與「熱狗」非常相似的食品 &mdash;「冰狗」，熱狗是將香腸夾在麵包中，而「冰狗」則是將雪糕取代香腸，夾在麵包中間，而此食品在推出沒多久，已經引來不少內地網民熱論。<br />\n<br />\n宜家美食站推出了新食品 &mdash; 「冰狗」，其英文名更是直接以中文翻譯成「Ice Dog」，售價為 3 元人民幣（約 HK$3.3）。而「冰狗」其實就是雪糕加上熱狗包，此款新奇有創意的食品吸引不少網民前往「打卡」，以及解鎖新食法。有網民更指「光看上去便覺得很好食」、「太有趣了，好想認識想到這個 Idea 的人」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:45:30.000Z","msg":"是咪暗串緊idog"},{"pid":"3b7751c915e835d3ee4223d242620fb337c11008","tid":2284133,"uid":64953,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7NXA9pX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7NXA9pX.jpg&h=13f9af3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁叫鰻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991ad03aa5aa636593d40765a8e36b1b4e601e05","tid":2284133,"uid":315771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:47:34.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢似撚狗"},{"pid":"8342b40435d3576bf318a18f88278fe218c50844","tid":2284133,"uid":372,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5f79137119da13297af006be63c08ad5313cd1db","tid":2284133,"uid":54373,"like":119,"dislike":2,"score":117,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:22:36.000Z","m